__section__
default
__description__
Creates a nice box with title and contents

* width = width of box (default is 200)
* contents = contents of box
* title = title of box
* center = boolean for centering box
* mainwidth = (not used here)
* insidewidth = (not used here)

__title__

__page__
misc
__lang__
en_US
__name__
fancybox
__template__
